    <p>With the publication of our newly created parish profile on our diocesean website, our search for a rector has begun. <%= link_to  "Click to download a copy of the profile", "http://res.cloudinary.com/saintpaulsnaples-org/image/upload/v1522935596/ParishProfile_vs6vjv.pdf.jpg.pdf" %> </p>
