      <p>The profile is among the documents that candidates receive in order to learn about our parish, and includes a brief history, our ministries and our desires.</p>
      <p>Input from a parish survey and the work of a long-range planning team was used as the basis, so parishioners' opinions and expressions are represented.</p>
      <p>If you know of a priest who would make a good rector for St. Paul's, get that person to read the profile and follow the procedure outlined for submission of materials to the diocese.</p>
      <p>The Rev. Canon Mike Durning, who knows our parish well, is helping us in this effort. </p> 
